    "html": "<h2>Chapter One: The Beginning</h2><p>It was a dark and stormy night. The wind howled through the empty streets of the old town, carrying with it whispers of ancient secrets long forgotten.</p><p>Sarah pulled her coat tighter and quickened her pace. She had been warned about nights like this, but the letter in her pocket was too important to ignore.</p><p>\"Just a few more blocks,\" she muttered to herself, glancing at the flickering streetlamps that seemed to dance in the wind.</p>",
